{"tid":2300720,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑自己係咪有病","createTime":"2020-11-25T17:40:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T03:58:58.000Z","uid":375643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"69747004f73c7f833585a4e46135efdf6664e625","tid":2300720,"uid":375643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T17:40:05.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪病黎<br />\n由今年5月開始, 成日訓教個陣有種好想屙尿既感覺, 要訓係張床過一段時間有尿意去屙尿先訓得著.<br />\n<br />\n之後就訓得斷斷續續, 隔幾個鐘醒一次, 醒左自己覺得要屙尿, 唔屙訓唔著, 屙完之後仲有尿意 要再屙幾次, 不過屙好少量, 無哂尿意先訓到. 不過有時覺得自己屙清哂 訓番係張床都訓唔著 失眠.<br />\n<br />\n但係以前可以一教訓到天光, 可以尿脹, 訓醒可以屙勁大篤. 唔知自己點解會咁 好奇怪<br />\n其實算唔算正常?? 你地係咪都同我一樣"},{"pid":"da124d8092c50bdc6062beb84114b3fcbe88a86c","tid":2300720,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T17:43:55.000Z","msg":"最近戒丁？"},{"pid":"28558e5de914953470ab658bfcceaa4bec2c61ac","tid":2300720,"uid":375643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da124d8092c50bdc6062beb84114b3fcbe88a86c","tid":2300720,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T17:43:55.000Z","msg":"最近戒丁？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T17:47:06.000Z","msg":"無戒<br />\n但唔係頻繁咁打"},{"pid":"f56036ac37e39e80d0c7511a82cdbeedc77fa8fd","tid":2300720,"uid":287784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T18:03:48.000Z","msg":"屙尿力度有無改變？"},{"pid":"f1ff33b2723e8f4b020877d9ac5edb18f11065f8","tid":2300720,"uid":106879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T18:07:56.000Z","msg":"試下訓教前2-3hr 唔好飲水"},{"pid":"40b5611dfd4c8c7777bc900b415d604de3d3ab07","tid":2300720,"uid":360183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T18:58:53.000Z","msg":"戒酒 咖啡"},{"pid":"faebe019efffd9208603d8123d8a2badf2761d6d","tid":2300720,"uid":375643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f56036ac37e39e80d0c7511a82cdbeedc77fa8fd","tid":2300720,"uid":287784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T18:03:48.000Z","msg":"屙尿力度有無改變？"},"citedB